text: Nexus One is a cell phone from Google that uses the Google Android operating system.Google Nexus One homepage It was made for Google by the HTC Corporation. == Technical information == The cell phone has a 1 GHz Qualcomm CPU, along with 512 MB RAM and 512 MB ROM. It has a 5.0 megapixel camera, with Bluetooth and GPS. It runs the Google Android 2.1 OS. ==Related pages== * Google Android * iPhone == References == Category:Nexus mobile phones Category:Android smartphones Category:Mobile phones introduced in 2010
title: Nexus One
